{"TopicId":213700,"ForumId":196,"TopicTitle":"Rotate the pod is affecting navbal and commands","CreatedByName":"Heady","CreatedById":226855,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:46:50Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Heady","CreatedById":226855,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:46:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:rgb(249,249,249);color:rgb(45,49,52);\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EKSP Version: 0.1.0.0.20892\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EOperating System and version \u00A0(Windows 10, Windows 11): Windows 19\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003EIntel i9, RTX 3090 TI\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EDescription of the bug. \u00A0\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ERotate the Vessel should not affect rotation on the navbal/commands\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EObserved Behavior: When you load any vehicule (e.g. Kerbal K1), then you rotate only the pod, it has some weird effects on the lauchpad, changing the orientation of the navbal as well as changing the commands\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ESteps to Replicate\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGo to \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli style=\u0022font-size:15px;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELoad Kerbal K1\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003ERotate only the pod by 180\u00B0\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003EGo to lauch pad\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003ECommands are now inverted as well as camera control and navbal. Rest of the map orientation hasn\u0027t changed\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003EBefore:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://ibb.co/kHtQ3sB\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://ibb.co/kHtQ3sB\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cb\u003EAfter:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://ibb.co/ZGLRh0z\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://ibb.co/ZGLRh0z\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/b\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:55:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWelcome to the forum \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/226855-heady/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022226855\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/226855-heady/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Heady\u003C/a\u003E, I\u0027m not sure this is a bug as this sounds like normal pod behavior\u00A0in KSP 1. The pods have a set orientation so that by default your rocket will use the \u0027d\u0027 key to steer east.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Heady","CreatedById":226855,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:57:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the navbal OK, but please reproduce and try to change camera orientation left an right, and see that it goes instead up and down\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"James Kerman","CreatedById":160462,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T16:59:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224246259\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022213700\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221677517027\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022226855\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Heady\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Heady said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the navbal OK, but please reproduce and try to change camera orientation left an right, and see that it goes instead up and down\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, that sounds like a bug to me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Heady","CreatedById":226855,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-02-27T17:21:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe it\u0027s easier with a gif. In both illustrations below i\u0027m doing right and left with my mouse\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBefore:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/h2xzgkn2c7qy0wc/before.gif?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/h2xzgkn2c7qy0wc/before.gif?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAfter:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.dropbox.com/s/4s0ukfkmb8htfzs/after.gif?dl=0\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.dropbox.com/s/4s0ukfkmb8htfzs/after.gif?dl=0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}